  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Several studies including ours have reported that celecoxib improves endothelium-dependent
      vasodilation and reduces inflammation and neointimal hyperplasia. Our hypothesis is that
      celecoxib may reduce the late luminal loss after coronary stent implantation
      (paclitaxel-eluting stent.
    </textblock>
